<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>能量代谢和体温 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/</link><description>Recent content in 能量代谢和体温 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 10:26:46 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>能量代谢</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 10:26:54 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2/</guid><description>&lt;p>机体的物质代谢包括合成代谢和分解代谢两个方面。通常将生物体内物质代谢过程中伴随发生的能量的释放、转移、储存和利用称为能量代谢。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>体温及其调节</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jul 2023 11:45:37 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B0%A2%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9/%E4%BD%93%E6%B8%A9%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E8%B0%83%E8%8A%82/</guid><description>&lt;p>通常将人体分为核心与表层两个部分。核心部分的温度称为体核温度；表层部分的温度称为体表温度。生理学或临床医学中所说的&lt;em>体温&lt;/em>通常是指机体核心部分的平均温度。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>体核温度不易测量，临床上通常用直肠（37.4 ± 0.5℃）、口腔（37.2 ± 0.5℃）和腋下（36.7 ± 0.7℃）等部位的温度来代表体核温度。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>